{"id": "1310533999948599316", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:think:1243504961254326354> 感覺太不新手(窮人)向了", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:14:14.132000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310534570445111298", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們可以先試想一下，如果你開場拿著超越之目，直接撿狂亂切割先清掉一些小怪甚至全殺，可以少挨幾下傷害保留健康血量\n\n只配塔薇的話就變成要先開縱橫時序才能暖機，還要二翼四翼開上去，當中不免就要犧牲一些血量與時間成本\n\n我從沒說塔薇不強，但這陣容本就是為注重攻擊而放棄防禦，而且塔薇的選卡環節是不是要搞死新手<:stoppage:1236938521365839872>", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:16:30.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310535017650192396", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "ㄟ....塔維直接去打菁英可以不爆死抗(X)", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:18:16.771000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310535050793848834", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "好啦，確實不太新手", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:18:24.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310535565636276234", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "479269844018135040", "author_name": "ekko9950", "author_bot": false, "content": "這與爆不爆死抗沒啥關係，是血肉塔薇會有別的配法，如果配塔薇的話就是艾繼絲與冬夜免了，因為前兩回合沒這麼容易灌傷害，直接把冬夜的效果浪費了", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:20:27.421000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310535827360714803", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "885882671899746305", "author_name": "cwz.io", "author_bot": false, "content": "塔薇C造價太高了<:cry:1239910167668326480>", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:21:29.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310536154168168478", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "我要組塔維肯定是混沌，如果是以血肉為出發點那情況當然不一樣", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:22:47.738000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1310536475552514110", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176198078026498098", "author_name": "huangyu0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "我說 不爆死抗的意思代表就算在最高難度塔維的輸出跟生存還是很強的，只要配隊有一定練度不會落地死那麼慘", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T09:24:04.362000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
